'''''Star Wars'' Celebration''' was the first [[Celebration]]. Intended to celebrate the history of ''[[Star Wars]]'' and promote the then-upcoming {{Film|I}}, the event was sponsored by [[Lucasfilm]] and organized by [[Dan Madsen]], president of the official ''Star Wars'' Fan Club, and held in [[Wikipedia:Denver, Colorado|Denver, Colorado]]&mdash;where the fan club was based at the time&mdash;at the [[Wikipedia:Wings Over the Rockies Air and Space Museum|Wings Over the Rockies Air and Space Museum]]. It was held over three days from [[April 30]] through [[May 2]], [[1999]].<ref name="SW.com2">{{SWArchive|url=community/event/celebration/f19990430/index.html|text=''Star Wars'' Celebration 1999}}</ref> 

